{"tid":1956258,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"渣打溫拓思批英美應對疫情反應太慢 未有效法中共的果措斷施","createTime":"2020-04-03T05:21:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T13:08:24.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d76188ecda22065d952cec57ce4196d68b0dfa27","tid":1956258,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T05:21:46.000Z","msg":"渣打溫拓思批英美應對疫情反應太慢<br />\n03.04.2020 11:42<br />\n<br />\n渣打集團(<a href=\"http://02888.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F02888.HK&d=HDFqBNw8TQCe%2BIc9lyi2BshAN7np5IU55thb9t6%2Bojg%3D&h=6767dc95\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">02888.HK</a>)行政總裁溫拓思接受接受《彭博電視》訪問時批評，英國及美國政府應對疫情反應太慢，未有如中國一樣採取果斷的封城措施。他指，聽到有意見反駁指西方或英美不能做到中國的處理方式，因為社會體制不同，但他認為目前英美亦跟隨中國的做法，只是做得太遲。他又認為，亞洲衛生部門，特別是中國、香港及新加坡，正示範如何在及早及硬性干預下能夠減慢病毒散播。<br />\n<br />\n英倫銀行早前要求，銀行在疫情爆發期間，不再向小股東支付股息，消息令渣打股價持續受壓，現跌逾3%，報38.55元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1278504&amp;csid=261_367\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1278504%26csid%3D261_367&d=HDFqBNw8TQCe%2BIc9lyi2BshAN7np5IU55thb9t6%2Bojg%3D&h=18a77031\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1278504&amp;csid=261_367</a>"},{"pid":"d1848c993d002e0d03c50562a0bcb585ebc01d18","tid":1956258,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T05:23:08.000Z","msg":"唔學肥仔金?<br />\n最最最WORK 一定係佢地"},{"pid":"b14c96ede9f82ea65f67769c4c15fe34b8fcaf89","tid":1956258,"uid":9542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T05:25:26.000Z","msg":"叫佢落武漢行一轉感受下果斷既成果先出黎講野"},{"pid":"16dffa40f2a0e41494bff1d1e2a2dd0c262de533","tid":1956258,"uid":199957,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T12:55:14.000Z","msg":"唔諗下點解反應慢? 傳到成個世界都係 仲話唔嚴重係邊隻力架講架"},{"pid":"435a9cabf8bbe6c0161f6908534805e8112632ac","tid":1956258,"uid":103916,"like":0,"dislike":0,